      • touch

        void touch()
        Deprecated. please update a field instead or set the bean version yourself
        Mark the bean as updated by forcing its version to change, even if no other fields have changed. For example, this can be useful for forcing validation or pre-update rules to run on a bean if only its sub beans have changed. WARNING: This sets the bean version to NULL which makes this bean instance the "current" version. If this bean is already retired, this will unretire the bean
